headline: The University of Melbourne Selects Rimini Street to Reduce Risk and Accelerate Innovation Around its Oracle Systems
summary: LAS VEGAS, July 23, 2025--Rimini Street, Inc. (Nasdaq: RMNI), a global provider of end-to-end enterprise software support, management and innovation solutions, and the leading third-party support provider for Oracle, SAP and VMware software, today announced that the top-ranking higher learning institute in Australia, The University of Melbourne, has engaged Rimini Street to enable greater digital innovation investments for its organization consisting of 55,000 students and 10,000 staff.
